Restaurant # 978-863-0121 (eva 978-857-6626)

Hit Squad is ready to rock the house at TJ Callahans(formerly The Backstage Grill) in Tewksbury… music and dance see the website for their great songlist under HitSquad band. Food is great here plenty of dancing space and plenty of parking space

Note might be a $3 cover will update closer to date, try to get your  rsvps in by end of Wed 1/25 so that us two gals can make  table reservations . 

Everyone is responsible for their own food/drink. PLEASE MAINTAIN YOUR OWN TAB OR PAY AS YOU ORDER AND TIP YOUR SERVERS!!

This event is shared with 5 other groups!!!

Band starts around 9pm-1am

 

Its Friday night yahoo so lets all go out and celebrate to a few great tunes see partial list or go on there website and find tons more.
